            <h1 class="abw_heading">Anti-Bullying Week</h1>
            <h2 class="abw_heading">Band together to beat bullying</h2>
            <h3>(18-22 November 2013)</h3>
            <p>
                BeatBullying's mission is to make bullying unacceptable - for
                everyone, everywhere - and we need your help to make this
                happen.
            </p>
            <p>
                Get involved during Anti-Bullying Week 2013: band together as a
                school or a class, or even take action as an individual. We've
                got loads of ideas on this site for what you can do.
            </p>
            <h3>Need help with bullying?</h3>
            <p>
                If you're a young person aged from 11-17, you can get help
                right now on
                <a href="http://beatbullying.org/">BeatBullying.org</a>.
                Talk to young people who have experienced the same issues or
                get specialist advice from our online counsellors.
            </p>
